<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#6c6c00">«٤»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(أبا نصر نوّر <span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> الشمس واظهر <span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> )</span> <span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> ... وخلّ الشّمس في سمك <span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> السّماك <span style="color:#6c6c00">«٥»</span> ) <span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
